[1] Samoa: case summary
Date: Sun 8 Dec 2019
Source: Government of Samoa @samoagovt [abridged, edited]
https://twitter.com/samoagovt/status/1203793768182235136


Latest update:
4693 measles cases have been reported since the outbreak with 112 recorded in the last 24 hours. To date, 70 measles related deaths have been recorded.

Age group / Measles cases last 24 hours / Total measles cases / Total measles related deaths
0-5 months / 3 / 335 / 9
